Package controllers

Package containing controllers that answer the different types of webservice requests.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    APIController
    Baseclass for controller classes
    Application
    Member login, registration and password reset functions
    AutoRun
    Automatically run plugins once a day for auto import of records
    AutoRun.Importer
    Akka actor that runs the plugin of a specific space
    AutoRun.ImportManager
    Akka actor that manages the import process
    AutoRun.ImportRequest
    request to run plugin for a specific space
    AutoRun.ImportResult
    response from import plugin for a space
    AutoRun.StartImport
    Start import message.
    Circles
    functions for managing consents
    Debug
    used for debugging.
    Developers

    FHIR

    FormatAPI
    used by portal to retrieve data groups
    Market
    functions for controlling the "market" of plugins
    MobileAPI
    functions for mobile APPs
    News

    OAuth2  
    Plugins
    functions for managing MIDATA plugins
    PluginsAPI
    API functions to be used by MIDATA plugins
    PortalConfig
    function for reading and writing the portal configuration of each user
    QuickRegistration  
    Records
    functions for handling the records
    Spaces
    functions for managing spaces (instances of plugins)
    Studies
    functions about studies.
    Tasking
    functions for managing user tasks
    UserGroups
    Management functions of user groups

    user related functions
